  "text": "Circular No. 20 / 2003-Cus. 27th March, 2003 No.450/ 24 /2003-Cus.IV Government of India Ministry of Finance & Company Affairs Department of Revenue (Central Board of Excise & Customs) Subject: Introduction of new stamps by the State Customs Service of Turkmenistan - reg. I am directed to enclose a copy of letter No.Ash/Misc/1/2003, dated the 17th February, 2003, along with its enclosures, received from Embassy of India, Ashgabat on the subject mentioned above for information and necessary action. D. S. Garbyal Under Secretary to the Govt. of India -- 1 of 1 --",
